            <title>[JCR-2741] Improved logging for session operations</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-2741</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>I&amp;#39;d like to add the following logging features to SessionOperations:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
* Use MDC [1] to make it possible to filter and redirect logs based on which session is being used&lt;br/&gt;
* Add simple debug-level timing information for executed SessionOperations to help pinpoint performance issues&lt;br/&gt;
* Classify SessionOperations as read or write operations, and log warnings (instead of the current debug messages) for concurrent writes on a session&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
[1] &lt;a href=&quot;http://logback.qos.ch/manual/mdc.html&quot;&gt;http://logback.qos.ch/manual/mdc.html&lt;/a&gt;</description>
